The overview of the COVID19 in World Wide From the figure 1 below, we can clearly observe the situation of COVID19 in various countries as of August 30th 2021. In order to better compare Kuwait, we use a separate color to distinguish. articles.title: COVID19 Blog
articles.description: This website is mainly used to record infection cases, deaths and other related data in some countries since the COVID-19 outbreak. We hope that through the changing trends of these data, we can gain insight into the impact of the epidemic on this country or region, and whether the government's control of the epidemic is effective.
